**Step 1**  
To import your posts from your [Blogger](https://www.blogger.com/),
  
you first have to [export the blog][export-blogger-xml]
to a XML file (`blog-MM-DD-YYYY.xml`), and run:  
$ ruby -rubygems -e 'require "jekyll-import";
JekyllImport::Importers::Blogger.run({
"source"=>"/path/to/blog-MM-DD-YYYY.xml",})'

The only required field is `source`.
  
The other fields default to their above values.

  
"Labels" will be included in export as "Tags".

  

注意:
1. ">"符號在Windows的cmd中要用^跳脫字符  
2. 必須載有Ruby環境，然後有它的bundler套件  
3. /_posts/裡的.md檔必須是Unix格式的換行(不得有\r)  
4. 中文編碼必須是UTF-8  

**Step 2**  
give_layout_to_tags.py:
將有特殊tag的post給予特殊layout

**Step 3**  
在主目錄裡輸入指令:
> jekyll build

**Step 4**  
p_tag_remover:  
在build完之後，從/zhhomstuck.github.io/p/中的html files中清除掉所有unintented tag  

**Step 5**  
將/page/裡的頁面放回/zhhomstuck.github.io/p/

**Step 6**  
make_raw_blog.py:  
將blog備份檔從很大的xml檔轉換成純文字的blog-raw.txt  